        femily_text: 'We invite women with a migration background to the excursion to Projekt Ada & Florence at BFI O√ñ ‚Äî digital skills and career orientation in IT (programming, apps, web). No prior computer knowledge required.\n\nüìç BFI Linz, Raimundstra√üe 1‚Äì5, 4020 Linz\nüóì Tuesday, 03.02.2026 ¬∑ 15:30‚Äì18:00\n\nProgramme: presentation of Ada & Florence, info on courses and career options.\n\nContact: Nahida Ezzo, Tel. 0676 8776 8002, nahida.ezzo@caritas-ooe.at\nwww.caritas-ooe.at/femily ‚Äî free of charge.'
